		       THE PAWN SOLUTION 

Taken from an ST SEWER SOFTWARE docs disk. This was worked out and Štyped in by SEWER POM. Edited by Parasite.


Look at your clothes.Go east.Say "Greetings" to Kronos.Take  note 
and  ask  Kronos  about wristband.Take  the  chest.Go  to  palace 
gardens  and look for a key.Look in the fountain.Go to  the  shed 
and  look  for a rake,hoe,trowel,and pot.Show  something  to  the 
guards.Go  to  the Guru.Cover the wristband and go to  the  large 
boulder.Tie  rake  and  hoe together with  your  shirt.Lever  the 
boulder with rake and hoe.Climb the rocks.When adventurer appears 
give him the chest.Get on the horse.Get some snow.Return to Guru.
     Go to the clearing and look at stump.Mix the items.Go to the 
large  tree.Unlock the door.Enter and close door.Lift boards  and 
go down stairs.From the staircase room go down to the low ceiling 
room.Go  west and southwest to lounge.Get the hard hat  and  wear 
it.Search the cushions for the coin.
     Go  to the lift and press button.Enter,close door and  press 
the   second   button.At  the  rockface  get   the   lumps   with 
trowel.Return to lift and press first button.Get the rope.
     Return to grassy plain.Buy whisky and beer bottles with coin 
and chit.Go to narrow track and climb over rocks.Go to the cavern 
and  find small cave.Go north.Go Go north to  labratory.Give  the 
rice and lumps to chemist.
     Examine tea chest and jars.Drink the liquid.Cast a spell  on 
the tomes.Go NE to the store room and get aerosol.Go SW,NW,W  and 
cross  rope bridge.Go NE to tunnel and N to room.Tear  the  paper 
wall with the trowel.
     Tie rope to the hook.Climb down.Keep knocking on  doors.Give 
porter whiskey bottle.Go E,D and N to the annexe.Give Jerry  beer 
bottle.Go S,E,N, and E to hell.
     Ask devil about wristband.Get potion bottle.Go to the dragon 
in the chamber via rope bridge and high ledge.In dragons  chamber 
shine  white at shadows.Go N.Throw potion bottle at  Kronos.Press 
nozzle.Look  inside  top hat.Examine rabbit and  rack.Get  pointy 
hat,wand and cloak.Wear cloak and hat.
     Go to hell where the devil waits.Give him the aerosol.Go  to 
entrance  by small cave near labratory.Open doors.Go  S.Knock  on 
door.Say NO.Go S.Examine listing.Type in the word DEBUG .
     Go to cavern near lava river.Move pedestal and get key.Go to 
snowman.Melt  him with white.Go to the store.Get spiky boots  and 
wear them.Get prism.Unlock door on landing....

ONCE  YOUVE EXAMINED THE LISTING AND TYPED DEBUG YOU CAN KEEP ON 
EXPERIMENTING AND EXPLORING WITHOUT GETTING KILLED

ALSO  BEFORE STARTING THE ADVENTURE TRY TYPING DEBUG AND GO PAST 
THE SOUTHERN EDGE OF THE ADVENTURE.